profile: We are a plumbing & general Contractor serving in the Perth & Ottawa area. We provide service as small as a plumbing leak to completing full kitchen or bathroom renovation. We are know for our craftsmanship work and honest spirt, we are able to offer 15-20 year warranty on our bathroom renovations. We remain a small company so not to lose our personal touch with our clients. Customer service is our main goal, we are here to turn your renovation dreams into reality.
